JMraidcon - JMB39x/JMS56x RAID Controller Tools

Command-line tools for managing JMicron JMB39x and JMS56x SATA
hardware RAID controllers without the X-based HWRaidManager.

Tools
-----
JMraidcon   Original tool - displays disk and RAID volume status
jmraidctl   Extended tool - adds management commands:
            - alarm-mute    Mute/unmute the RAID alarm
            - identify      Blink disk LED for identification
            - standby       Set disk standby timer (0-255 minutes)
            - rebuild-priority  Set rebuild priority
            - rebuild-status    Show rebuild progress

Usage
-----
  ./jmraidctl /dev/sgX                  Show RAID status
  ./jmraidctl /dev/sgX alarm-mute 1     Mute alarm
  ./jmraidctl /dev/sgX identify 0 1     Blink disk 0 LED
  ./jmraidctl /dev/sgX standby 30       30-minute standby timer
  ./jmraidctl /dev/sgX rebuild-priority medium
  ./jmraidctl /dev/sgX rebuild-status

Building
--------
  make

